Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-------------------OP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.49,0:01:43.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你剛才在唱歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.83,0:01:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs37}雖然想去取預定的校服
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.40,0:01:47.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs37}但是店面的位置怎麼都找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.39,0:01:50.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs37}所以從早上開始就一直在這附近晃悠了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.12,0:01:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs37}但是能遇到大家真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.22,0:01:47.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 有在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.07,0:01:50.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡的店
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.60,0:01:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,車站的可樂餅店
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.31,0:01:53.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.92,0:01:53.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs37}對了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.72,0:01:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從今往後能直接叫大家的名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.06,0:02:00.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs37}可以的話直呼我名字的話我會很開心的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.63,0:01:57.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同學接下來有什麼打算麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.92,0:01:59.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有 正準備回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.60,0:02:00.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然你剛才唱歌了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.04,0:02:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是毀也納來著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.02,0:02:03.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 是維也納
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.41,0:02:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.96,0:02:05.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs37}毀也納
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.18,0:02:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs37}維也納
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.87,0:02:09.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唱了吧 是唱歌了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.07,0:02:10.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毀也納
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.84,0:02:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,維也納
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.73,0:02:12.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是毀也納吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.74,0:02:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了 是哪個都沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,田中給毀也納帶下路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.27,0:02:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,維也納
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.85,0:02:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毀也納？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.23,0:02:21.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 坂井同學 要不要來我家轉轉？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.96,0:02:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沖田同學家？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,----------------------------------------
