Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.94,0:02:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs74\c&H000000&\blur2\shad5\3c&HB8B8C4&\fad(640,0)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\b0\i1\pos(584,478)\4c&H606060&}焦躁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.29,0:02:47.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紗羽 來夏醬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.54,0:02:49.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aloha—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.54,0:02:49.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs37}Aloha：夏威夷土語裡的招呼語
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.79,0:02:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 志保姐 是去海邊麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:54.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 那個是你們的朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.58,0:02:58.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 同一個班級的坂井和奏同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.49,0:03:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 好好玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.28,0:03:03.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那晚飯前我會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.36,0:03:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aloha—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.08,0:03:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.94,0:03:07.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.96,0:03:12.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 薩布萊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.30,0:03:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多吃點然後長得壯壯的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.82,0:03:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.14,0:03:17.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說啥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:18.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼有馬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:20.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我在養馬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.09,0:03:22.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.63,0:03:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:27.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.08,0:03:28.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.33,0:03:30.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉啊 一股銅錢臭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.39,0:03:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沖田同學家 是開寺廟的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.60,0:03:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 叫我紗羽就好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.94,0:03:42.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個 有看過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.50,0:03:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去年的共同發表會的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.94,0:03:47.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.32,0:03:49.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 來夏在這
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.98,0:03:53.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為太緊張了所以唱不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.29,0:04:05.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 忍不住又笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.87,0:04:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果太緊張唱不出來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:13.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明假裝在唱就能混過去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.66,0:04:15.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到最後為止都不放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:18.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從結果上來說雖然是大失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.25,0:04:20.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我很喜歡喲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.39,0:04:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為不管看幾遍都會笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 開玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.18,0:04:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 坂井
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在合唱部只是借個名字可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:41.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為不想把這個變成最後一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從去年開始一直特訓到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.91,0:04:47.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有一點機會的話也需要能幫助她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.59,0:04:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託 因為要成立社團怎麼都得五個人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.69,0:04:54.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算只是形式上的也可以 不行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.57,0:04:58.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太糾纏的話 又會被罵的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.47,0:05:02.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是借個名字的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.11,0:05:03.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.42,0:05:05.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.77,0:05:10.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩子還真是難懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:12.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休息的日子穿著奇怪的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:14.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪的衣服？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.38,0:05:16.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 要一起吃飯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.07,0:05:18.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我家現在就我和姐姐兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.85,0:05:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有能好好做飯的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.78,0:05:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個 難道是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.89,0:05:29.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切薄片的牛肉和蔬菜甜辣口味燉煮的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.23,0:05:30.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日本的基本料理
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.13,0:05:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 這就是壽喜燒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.37,0:05:38.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是牛肉蓋澆飯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:42.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃完了飯 一起去買本正經點的書吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.93,0:05:50.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 先讓弟弟去邀請下朋友如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.27,0:05:51.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個不錯 採用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.01,0:05:54.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起舞的小提琴家 熊谷哲二會來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.38,0:05:57.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,募集以那個為目的想參加的人這樣的如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:05:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個也採用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.06,0:05:59.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.98,0:06:01.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用很奇怪的方法拉琴的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.62,0:06:06.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 讓志保姐幫忙做一下募集部員的傳單吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.39,0:06:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託那種事會讓她太得意的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.54,0:06:14.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母親經常被拜託畫宣傳畫和傳單什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.74,0:06:17.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,志保姐的畫 很有震撼力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.77,0:06:27.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.98,0:06:30.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了別這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.51,0:06:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,記得也邀請下你的朋友去合唱部哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:35.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈 才不會邀請呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:39.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藏限制級書的地方 換了也沒用哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.25,0:06:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.07,0:06:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多多關照 我們是合唱部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.73,0:06:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請拿傳單看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是合唱部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.13,0:06:58.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Good Job
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.13,0:07:02.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 當然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.88,0:07:06.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於那件事的話 會在下一次理事會進行報告
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.33,0:07:10.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 先失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.41,0:07:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 先掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.16,0:07:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.22,0:07:33.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.11,0:07:37.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去聲樂部不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.37,0:07:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 所以說那裡不讓我唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.26,0:07:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且部員也都募集好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.35,0:07:45.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與聲樂部不同
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.51,0:07:48.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用新的概念在共同發表會裡出場
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.45,0:07:49.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定會引起好的刺激...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教頭老師估計有她自己的想法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.79,0:07:57.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臨時拼湊的成員參加發表會什麼的...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.38,0:08:03.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？ 說不定挺有趣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 去參加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:11.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為我們學校的特別隊刺激音樂課學生的成長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.83,0:08:14.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顧問就由我來擔任可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:16.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.53,0:08:20.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,始終對你們學生的潛力和可能性充滿信心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.07,0:08:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是這樣的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.37,0:08:25.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:30.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.83,0:08:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We interested in...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:09:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宮本同學 你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:13.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 每一支箭都要慎重的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.41,0:09:14.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.13,0:09:17.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合唱部那邊什麼時候開始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.64,0:09:20.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從明天午休開始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.52,0:09:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.70,0:09:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本來想先把曲目定下來的說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.73,0:09:28.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是光看樂譜完全沒辦法想像出來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:33.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我知道 其他人不知道也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.46,0:09:38.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算明天大家集合時儘快確定曲目開始排練
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:43.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同學你會彈鋼琴啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.37,0:09:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為音樂科鋼琴是必修課
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.03,0:09:49.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然彈得沒專攻鋼琴的那麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.72,0:09:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同學 雖然約好只是來掛名的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.85,0:09:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今明兩天確定曲目前能不能來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.46,0:09:58.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正式演出和平時的排練怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.79,0:10:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我弟弟正在邀請會電子琴的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.19,0:10:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想快點確定曲目
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕練習時間多一天也好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.34,0:10:07.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了 我請你吃蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.77,0:10:09.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋糕兩個！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.35,0:10:12.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.73,0:10:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太感謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼把這些按順序彈一遍看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.74,0:10:21.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是高潮部份就行了吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.03,0:10:23.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給 首先是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.81,0:10:24.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有點奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.49,0:10:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,封面上有被塗鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.93,0:10:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歌也完全沒聽過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.59,0:10:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樂譜還是手寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:55.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好喜歡這首曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:57.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有點像Condor Queens的風格
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.02,0:11:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道麼？ 雖然是以前的樂隊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:02.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次借CD給你聽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.49,0:11:03.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.53,0:11:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這首曲子也許不錯呢 再來一遍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.86,0:11:07.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次從頭開始彈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.00,0:11:08.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.79,0:11:43.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果沒有異議的話 發表會就用這首曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.52,0:11:48.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部長 排練幾點開始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有課外補習 如果太晚的話有點...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.24,0:11:52.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.97,0:11:55.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宮本同學 那麼我就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.08,0:11:57.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.95,0:12:01.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那請大家寫下希望的時間交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:02.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然距離發表會時間所剩不多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.41,0:12:08.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是好好練習完成讓全場一鳴驚人的歌曲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.35,0:12:23.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經得到校長的許可了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.58,0:12:24.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.47,0:12:25.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曲目呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這首曲子沒辦法通過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再找別的曲子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.83,0:12:38.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼能這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.73,0:12:41.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會很困擾的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.48,0:12:46.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是你們可以拿來唱著玩的曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.35,0:12:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.77,0:12:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然從來沒有聽過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.19,0:12:56.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是作曲的人享受音樂的心情傳達給了我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.27,0:13:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十分的率直 很認真的喜歡著歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.50,0:13:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是果然還是很享受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:06.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能把我現在的心情完全安撫的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.99,0:13:10.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想唱這首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.37,0:13:14.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自娛自樂和給人帶去快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.65,0:13:18.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩邊兼顧 那種事情你做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,----------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插曲（同ED）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,----------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.43,0:14:05.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紗羽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.58,0:14:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,校長來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.83,0:14:09.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒 也沒有任何聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.59,0:14:12.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不知道有沒有別的能開車的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.50,0:14:15.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有顧問老師的帶領的話就回去上課吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.02,0:14:19.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有顧問或者副顧問老師的帶領的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.87,0:14:21.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁止進行校外社團活動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.18,0:14:25.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你作為部長好歹應該知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.02,0:14:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是......
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.19,0:14:27.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,副顧問是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.87,0:14:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是高橋老師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.92,0:14:32.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去聯繫看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:35.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你留在這裡跟部員一起等著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.13,0:14:39.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相對的找個人去參加上午的彩排
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.54,0:14:41.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那誠去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.46,0:14:42.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.05,0:14:45.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你會認樂譜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.01,0:14:51.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 現在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.27,0:14:57.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教頭主任說非坂井同學不可
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.51,0:15:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.63,0:15:05.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是部員的聲部和站位
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.17,0:15:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都寫在紙上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.49,0:15:08.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有這是樂譜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.48,0:15:11.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有事的話手機聯絡我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.62,0:15:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這邊的情況也會及時通知你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.48,0:15:16.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的...很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.91,0:15:22.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋糕 兩個哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.43,0:15:29.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高橋老師不接電話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.14,0:15:30.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去她家看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.52,0:15:31.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.90,0:15:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 蠻近的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是校長來了的話讓大巴途中接我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.03,0:15:46.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊...有點緊張了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:15:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.33,0:15:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊...那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.69,0:16:02.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是智子的學生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.86,0:16:04.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 那個...老師在麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去醫院接受體檢了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.25,0:16:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是哪家醫院呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.74,0:16:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宮本同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.52,0:16:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到校長了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.73,0:16:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.19,0:16:27.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 彩排已經開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.65,0:16:29.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那邊沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:33.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然找到校長了 但是具體情況還不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.42,0:16:34.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在和多田老師一起...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.18,0:16:35.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs37}白浜坂高中合唱部的同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.41,0:16:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:37.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.63,0:16:39.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對會到的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.86,0:16:47.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我當時停下了的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.85,0:16:49.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明才打上蠟不久
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.18,0:16:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自行車也要打上蠟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.56,0:16:54.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是這樣的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.96,0:16:54.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,校長！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:55.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你懂了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.94,0:17:05.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.99,0:17:08.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊咧 沖田
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.37,0:17:09.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.36,0:17:10.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懷孕了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.12,0:17:12.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.92,0:17:15.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,校長去不了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.08,0:17:16.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來不了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.79,0:17:18.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是已經幫忙聯繫了學校
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.38,0:17:19.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大巴已經出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該能趕得上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.06,0:17:24.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們也趕去會場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.38,0:17:26.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 你現在在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.28,0:17:28.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在在醫院 接下來...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.38,0:17:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs37}來夏？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.52,0:17:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在這裡啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.23,0:17:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出場的順序
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:36.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能請您把合唱部放在最後
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:39.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在正在趕過來 肯定會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.43,0:17:42.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我知道突然的變更困難...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.64,0:17:45.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛校長跟我聯繫過了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.91,0:17:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.89,0:17:48.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然這不是我的本意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.36,0:17:51.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你們發表排在聲樂部之後了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.01,0:17:52.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝您了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.57,0:17:57.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.44,0:17:59.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是勉強能趕上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.76,0:18:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.19,0:18:02.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的部員已經過去了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.15,0:18:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在正在往那邊趕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.62,0:18:05.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有坂井已經先去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.19,0:18:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.30,0:18:09.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.10,0:18:13.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇—哇—哇—哇—哇—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.97,0:18:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嚇死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.59,0:18:16.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要出事故的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.87,0:18:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做了那麼多特訓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經跟去年不一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放鬆 放鬆 放鬆 放鬆 放鬆...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs37}接下來由白浜坂高中合唱部發表心的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.52,0:18:33.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宮本同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:34.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.79,0:18:35.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.67,0:18:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點 播報員已經開始報幕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.03,0:18:41.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的成員已經上去了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？沒有跟你一起嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.16,0:18:44.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:48.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總算脫離堵車路段了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.76,0:18:50.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還需要一點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.50,0:18:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在你那邊什麼情況啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.03,0:18:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能趕上嗎？ 姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.28,0:18:59.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去聯絡中止發表
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.05,0:19:06.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.15,0:19:11.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一個人牽扯了這麼多人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.26,0:19:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備什麼都不做就回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.89,0:19:13.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不覺得不甘心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.73,0:19:16.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經沒有下次了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.39,0:19:21.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎麼忘了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.17,0:19:24.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去年的恥辱 必須好好的彌補回來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.63,0:19:26.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我管他呢 唱歌就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.07,0:19:28.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算丟臉也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.63,0:19:29.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走到哪裡算哪裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.14,0:19:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.00,0:19:35.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫這麼多忙謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.65,0:19:38.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去把之前問題的答案找來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.99,0:19:40.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.15,0:19:42.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你為了什麼而唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.04,0:19:45.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.61,0:19:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 唱一首然後回家吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0,0,0,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.71,0:20:08.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.67,0:20:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:13.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當成是南瓜田就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.68,0:20:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒見過南瓜田呃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:19.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那當成西瓜田呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.83,0:20:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還真是失禮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.61,0:20:31.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？坂井同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.28,0:20:36.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.03,0:20:38.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.25,0:20:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是說三塊蛋糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.19,0:20:43.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-------------------ED-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.54,0:23:23.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我暫時要住院一陣子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.84,0:23:27.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此期間就拜託你擔任校長代理了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.73,0:23:28.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.82,0:23:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我紗羽就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.17,0:23:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大君？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.24,0:23:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果要做的話 就想要贏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.71,0:23:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請讓我們在這裡唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.25,0:23:39.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要是贏了你們兩個就要進入羽毛球部哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.73,0:23:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-------------------OPJ-------------------
Dialogue: 1,0:00:27.50,0:00:30.00,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}胸の奥が高鳴る
Dialogue: 1,0:00:30.63,0:00:33.47,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}熱い声に気付いたら
Dialogue: 1,0:00:33.51,0:00:35.72,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}スタートラインは
Dialogue: 1,0:00:36.26,0:00:38.72,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}君の目の前にある
Dialogue: 1,0:00:38.97,0:00:41.35,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}まだ見えない道でも
Dialogue: 1,0:00:42.10,0:00:44.85,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}走り始めればいいさ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:44.89,0:00:47.06,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}諦めるよりも
Dialogue: 1,0:00:47.73,0:00:50.19,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}素敵だと思わない？
Dialogue: 1,0:00:50.48,0:00:55.28,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}いつも不安はすぐ傍で
Dialogue: 1,0:00:55.32,0:01:01.20,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}駆け出す思いを 締め付けるけれど
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.33,0:01:04.50,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}今を越えて 歩き出す
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.54,0:01:07.25,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}未知なる道に光を
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.29,0:01:10.21,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}初めてを 繰り返し
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.25,0:01:12.84,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}掴み取れ 明日を
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.88,0:01:15.97,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}さっさと友達が無限の
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.01,0:01:18.64,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}夢抱きしめ 進むのさ
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.72,0:01:24.56,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}輝いてる自分を信じていい
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.64,0:01:27.35,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}立ち上がる力に
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.44,0:01:30.19,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}盛大の愛を込めて
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.27,0:01:32.94,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}思うまま 旅立とう
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.98,0:01:38.95,opj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}新しい世界の中へ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-------------------OPC-------------------
Dialogue: 1,0:00:27.50,0:00:30.00,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}胸口傳出響亮的聲響
Dialogue: 1,0:00:30.63,0:00:33.47,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}希望有誰能夠注意到這熱忱的聲音
Dialogue: 1,0:00:33.51,0:00:35.72,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}人生的Start Line
Dialogue: 1,0:00:36.26,0:00:38.72,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}無時無刻都會出現在你的眼前
Dialogue: 1,0:00:38.97,0:00:41.35,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}即使是看不到盡頭的道路
Dialogue: 1,0:00:42.10,0:00:44.85,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}只要踏出第一步就是前進
Dialogue: 1,0:00:44.89,0:00:47.06,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}比起直接放棄
Dialogue: 1,0:00:47.73,0:00:50.19,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}不覺得這樣更好嗎？
Dialogue: 1,0:00:50.48,0:00:55.28,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}不安總是徘徊在我們的身旁
Dialogue: 1,0:00:55.32,0:01:01.20,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}將這份鼓動的心情 關閉在深處的抽屜裡
Dialogue: 1,0:01:01.33,0:01:04.50,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}讓我們邁出腳步越過現在
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.54,0:01:07.25,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}照亮那條未知的道路
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.29,0:01:10.21,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}不斷重複著將終點轉變為起點
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.25,0:01:12.84,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}用我們的雙手抓住未來
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.88,0:01:15.97,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}趕快集結起夥伴
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.01,0:01:18.64,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}擁抱無限的夢想 向前推進
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.72,0:01:24.56,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}鼓起勇氣相信閃耀著的自己吧
Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.64,0:01:27.35,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}將盛大的愛灌注進乾涸的心靈
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.44,0:01:30.19,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}給再次站起來的力量
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.27,0:01:32.94,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}就讓我們任著性子去旅行吧
Dialogue: 1,0:01:32.98,0:01:38.95,opc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\blur3}讓我們換乘進入新的世界
